en_50682_0	The MDMK has announced that it would release videos and pamphlets in multiple languages highlighting alleged atrocities committed during the war in Sri Lanka.
en_50682_1	The MDMK's plan was outlined by its chief Vaiko during a news conference yesterday.
en_50682_2	He further said the MDMK would approach commoners, public figures and politicians for their support.
en_50682_3	Our news tam contacted the Director of the Media Centre for National security Lakshman Hulugalla with regard to this issue.
en_50682_4	The Director stated that he is unable to make a statement since he has not received any official information.
